'''Sekhukhune'' goba '''Matsebe Sekhukhune''', (1814â€“1882), ebe ele ngwana wa mathomo go ba bararo ba kgoshi Sekwati le Thorometjane.Barwa ba Kgoshi Sekwati ke Sekhukhune (Matsebe),Dinkwanyane le Kgoloko.Ka setjo sa Bapedi bogoshi bo tjea ka ngwana wa pele ka morago ga lehu la tatagwe.Matsebe (Sekhukhune) o rile ka morago ga lehu la tatagwe (Sekwati) ka 1861,a latela setjo sa sepedi ka ge Tatagwe e be ele kgoshi.O thopile bogoshi go morwarragwe Mampuru ka lerumo.Mampuru yeo lehono baretjego (Pretoria central prison) ka yena,e be e le morwarrago Sekhukhune ka ge mmagwe (Kgomomakatane) a nyetjwe ke bakgomana ba ga Sekwati.Mampuru o godishitjwe ke  mmago Sekhukhune (Thorometjane) ka lapeng la moshate.

Ge Hendrik Potgieter le masole a gagwe (Voortrekkes)ba sahlela moshate wa bapedi ka pshiring ka 1838 .Sekwati o ba fentje mara a tla a lemoga gore moshate wa gagwe wa pshiring ga se wa bolokega ke ge a tlo khudugela  Thaba mosego (Leolo).

Sekhukhune I,ebe ele kgoshi kgolo ya [[Bapedi]] (goba Marota) ba [[Sekhukhune|ga Sekhukhune]], [[Limpopo]] nageng ya [[Afrika Borwa]].O be a dula ko thabeng ya Leolo,<ref>{{cite book|last = du Plessis|first = E.J. |coauthors = |title = Suid-Afrikaanse berg- en rivier name|publisher = Tafelberg-uitgewers, Cape Town |year = 1973|pages = 187|isbn = 0-624-00273-X}}</ref> e ago kgona go e shireletja.kgoshi kgolo Sekhukhune naga ya gagwe e thoma ka noka ya Lekwe,south(vaal river), go fihla ka noka ya Lebepe,north (limpopo river) gape Mogomatse,east(komati river) le kgalagadi,west (Bophirima).Sechaba sa Bapedi sebopa ke mehlobo ya Batau (Manganeng,Masemola,Mogashoa),Bakgaga (Mphahlele,Kopa,Maake),Baroka (Malatjie,Ratau,Mashishi,
Phasa),Bakwena,Mapulana,Bakone (Matlala),Moletlane,Batswako,Batlokwa,Balobedu ,Molapo,Molepo,Dikgale le babangwe.Mehlobo e mengwe e hwetjagalago ka nageng ya ga Sekhukhune,ke Matebele,Matsonga,Maswatsi le Vavenda.Magoshi a ga Sekhukhune ka Palo 167 le Dintona tje 268.

Ba bodikela (Makgowa) barile ge  bafihla mo nageng ya ga Sekhukhune ba e abaganya Kage babe banyaka mahumo a naga(gauta) babe baerela leina la Transvaal,ge go fihla maisemane ba e a abaganya gape ba e bitja TWV (Transvaal,Witwatersrant and Vereeniging).Kgoshi kgolo Sekhukhune o lwetje naga ya gagwe goba go fihla Maburu le Maisemane ba kopana ba dira seboka gore ba kgone goka fenya Sekhukhune.

Sekhukhune o kgonne go fenya ntwa magareng ga Maburu le Maesimane bale seboka .Goba go fihla Maburu le Maisemane ba eya gohloma seboka sesengwe le Maswatsi ke ge ba kgona go moswara ba moisha ko toronkong ya Pitori(Tswane)

Leshika la kgoro ya Sekhukhune.
